Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:22.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WONDER...\NWHERE DID I GO WRONG?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WONDER...\NWHEN DID EVERYTHING CHANGE?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:28.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF I COULD DO IT\NALL OVER AGAIN,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.16,Main,,0,0,0,,IF I WAS ONLY\NGIVEN THE CHANCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:34.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: EVER SINCE THE MOMENT\NI SAW HIS SHOULDERS TREMBLING.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT DAY, THAT PLACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:41.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WANT TO SET HER FREE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE SHOULDN'T BE\NHELD CAPTIVE BY THIS ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, HE'S WRONG.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE I KNOW THERE'S\NMORE TO IT THAN THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,IN THE END,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I FOUND SOMETHING\NMORE IMPORTANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- Both: I REMEMBER.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( theme music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- DID YOU HEAR THERE'S A WHIZ\NKID IN MINAZUKI ELEMENTARY?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.32,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT RUMOR SNAKED ITS WAY\NTHROUGH THE SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,SEVERAL YEARS AGO.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,THE WHIZ KID IN QUESTION\NWAS INDEED SOMEWHAT SMARTER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,THAN THE OTHER STUDENTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,ON TOP OF THAT,\NHE WAS UNUSUALLY FOCUSED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.84,Main,,0,0,0,,AND A DILIGENT HARD WORKER.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.30,Main,,0,0,0,,ALL THE ADULTS\NSANG HIS PRAISES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:54.84,Main,,0,0,0,,AND HAD UNDERSTANDABLY\NHIGH HOPES FOR HIM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.68,Main,,0,0,0,,THEN ONE DAY...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU ARE AMAZING, YUUJI.\N- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE TEACHER KEPT\NBRAGGING ABOUT YOUR SCORES
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:12.28,Main,,0,0,0,,ON THE PREP TEST.\NSHE CALLED YOU A BOY WONDER.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU SAY THAT LIKE\NI SHOULD CARE OR SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- DIDN'T YOU GET\NEVEN BETTER SCORES
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,THAN THE KIDS FROM\NJUNIOR HIGH?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, I GUESS.\N- SEE, THAT'S AMAZING.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.28,Main,,0,0,0,,THOSE SIXTH GRADERS\NWHO TOOK THE TEST WITH YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,WERE NOT HAPPY\NABOUT IT EITHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:26.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- I MADE A MISTAKE\NON THE SOCIAL SCIENCE TEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.12,Main,,0,0,0,,OTHERWISE I WOULD HAVE\NBEEN NUMBER ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: BACK THEN, I ALWAYS\NWANTED TO BE THE BEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I NEEDED IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- Young Shouko: I HEARD\NYOU'RE GOING TO GET ADMITTED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,TO THE BEST\NJUNIOR HIGH AROUND
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,ON A RECOMMENDATION ALONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, EASY ENOUGH FOR ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,THOUGH, MOST OTHER KIDS\NWON'T STAND A CHANCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: UNFORTUNATELY,\NI HAD AN EGO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT WAS COMPLETELY INTERTWINED\NWITH A SUPERIORITY COMPLEX.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- WILL YOU PLEASE\NKEEP WORKING, SHOUKO?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I WANT TO FINISH THIS\NSO I CAN GO HOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:03:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I WAS HOPING\NWE COULD STAY HERE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,AND TALK FOR AWHILE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WANT TO GO HOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT I WANT TO TALK.\N- I DON'T.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES.\N- I SAID NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES.\N- NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU WANT TO KNOW SOMETHING?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I THINK MY BOOBS ARE\NGETTING BIGGER AND BIGGER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:20.93,Main,,0,0,0,,EVERY DAY.\N- ( grunts )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,\NYUUJI?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- SERIOUSLY? WHERE IN THE\NHELL DID THAT COME FROM?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU WERE ATTEMPTING\NTO IGNORE ME,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I DECIDED TO\NBRING UP SOMETHING
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,A BOY WOULD FIND\NINTERESTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- NICE TRY,\NBUT I STILL DON'T CARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:36.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: THAT MAY NOT\NHAVE BEEN ENTIRELY TRUE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- WILL YOU PLEASE JUST\NGET BACK TO WORK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T MIND WORKING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.95,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I WANT TO TALK\NWITH YOU TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T YOU EVER\NTALK TO YOUR FRIENDS?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES.  THAT IS EXACTLY\NWHAT I'M TRYING TO DO NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, LUCKY ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji:\NSHOUKO DIDN'T QUITE FIT IN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,WITH THE REST OF THE SCHOOL.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE CAME FROM\NA WELL-KNOWN FAMILY,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.30,Main,,0,0,0,,WAS AT THE TOP OF HER CLASS,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,HAD INCREDIBLE\NATHLETIC TALENT,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.55,Main,,0,0,0,,AND OF COURSE,\NWAS BEAUTIFUL.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE WAS THE LUCKY ONE,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,AND EVERYONE\NRESENTED HER FOR IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:08.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- GOOD MORNING.\NMY NAME IS SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( kids murmuring )
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- HMM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- DUDE, YOU SHOULD\NGO TALK TO HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY? YOU'RE THE ONE\NWHO WANTS TO, YOU BUTT HEAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH. I THINK YOU WANT HER TO\NBE YOUR VERY FIRST GIRLFRIEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO I DON'T.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, WHAT DO YOU THINK?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,IS THAT KIRISHIMA GIRL\NTRYING TO ACT TOO CUTE?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:41.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- HER FAMILY'S RICH.\NI BET SHE'S A SPOILED PRINCESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE'S NOT EASY TO TALK TO,\NTHAT'S FOR SURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- Students: I KNOW, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: WITH THE WAY ALL\NTHOSE KIDS BEHAVED TOWARDS HER,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S NO WONDER SHOUKO\NENDED UP GETTING ATTACHED TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,AFTER ALL,\NI TREATED EVERYONE THE SAME,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.90,Main,,0,0,0,,NO MATTER WHAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO IT'S ALREADY\NBEEN TWO YEARS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,SINCE YOU TRANSFERRED\NTO THIS SCHOOL, HASN'T IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH.  I HAVE MORE FRIENDS\NNOW THAN I DID BACK THEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T HAVE A WHOLE LOT,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT SCHOOL'S MORE FUN\NTHAN IT USED TO BE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:13.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT.  YOU THINK\NSCHOOL IS FUN?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, WHEN I'M AT HOME,\NNO ONE PLAYS WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,OR EVEN TALKS TO ME\NFOR THE MOST PART.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THE HOUSE IS SO BIG,\NI GET LONELY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.09,Main,,0,0,0,,SO, YEAH.\NSCHOOL IS FUN IN COMPARISON.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- JEEZ.\NCRY ME A RIVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I WISH I COULD FEEL\NLONELY AND SAD
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,IN A BIG HOUSE LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU CAN COME HANG OUT\NAT MY HOUSE IF YOU WANT TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T. IT'S LIKE 100\NTIMES MORE FUN READING
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,THAN HANGING OUT WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: THAT WAS MEAN.\N- JUST BEING HONEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: STICK IN THE MUD.\N- SAY WHATEVER YOU WANT TO SAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: PIG-HEADED.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- KEEP IT UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YUUJI?\N- HMM?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THINK YOU MIGHT HAVE\NA LITTLE CRUSH ON ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,AND BECAUSE OF THAT, YOU'RE TOO\NNERVOUS TO HANG OUT AT MY HOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY DO YOU WANT ME\NTO GO TO YOUR HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,SO BADLY\NIN THE FIRST PLACE?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, WHAT?\NSPIT IT OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY GRANDFATHER\NTALKS ABOUT SENDING ME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,TO AN ALL-GIRLS'\NACADEMY A LOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT THAT\NFAMOUS RICHY SCHOOL FOR CHICKS?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.09,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU GONNA\NCHANGE SCHOOLS AGAIN?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- PROBABLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.18,Main,,0,0,0,,HE SEEMS TO THINK\NI GET PICKED ON
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,MORE THAN MOST KIDS\NAT SCHOOL DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO YOU WANT TO SHOW OFF\NYOUR FRIENDS TO YOUR FAMILY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,SO THEY WON'T THINK\NYOU'RE LONELY AND MISERABLE?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T WANT TO\NCHANGE SCHOOLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I ACTUALLY HAVE MADE SOME\NFRIENDS BESIDES YOU,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,SO YOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEN TAKE THOSE WEIRDOES\NTO YOUR HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'RE NOT CLOSE ENOUGH\NFOR THAT YET.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,WELL, EITHER WAY, THAT'S GOT\NNOTHING TO DO WITH ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: I TREATED EVERYONE\NTHE SAME NO MATTER WHAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS EQUALLY UNINTERESTED\NIN ALL OF THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,AT LEAST,\NTHAT'S WHAT I TOLD MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT WAS MEAN, YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, IT WASN'T.\N- WAS TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAS NOT.\N- WAS TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAS NOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI.\N- HMM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- IN OUR ENTIRE CLASS,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'VE GOT THE BIGGEST\NOF THE BOOBIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( Young Yuuji grunts )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,SHOUKO!\N- Yuuji: EVEN SO,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,THE ATTENTION I GAVE\NSEEMED TO BE ENOUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR A GIRL WHO HAPPENED\NTO BE VERY LONELY.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S UP, SAKAMOTO?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( boys panting )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHERE DO YOU THINK\NYOU'RE GOING, FREAK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE GOT SOMETHING\NWE WANT TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:31.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THIS IS WHY I WANTED\NTO HEAD HOME EARLIER.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?\NCAN'T HEAR YOU, TURD.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- TURD, REALLY?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:40.85,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DO YOU ALL WANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T HAVE TIME\NTO WASTE ON A BUNCH OF LOSERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHUT UP! TRY AND HAVE A LITTLE\NRESPECT FOR YOUR ELDERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- SURE ARE A SMART ASS\NFOR A FIFTH GRADE BABY.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.03,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'VE BEEN WAITING FOR THIS\NSINCE I BEAT YOUR SCORES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,ON THAT TEST, HAVEN'T YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,DON'T YOU HAVE ANYTHING\NBETTER TO DO,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.91,Main,,0,0,0,,LIKE FRIENDS\NTO HANG OUT WITH?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,OR MAYBE YOU GUYS\NARE TOO PATHETIC
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,TO HAVE ANY FRIENDS.\N- ( boys gasp )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH, NO.  YOU'RE THE ONE\NWHO DOESN'T HAVE ANY FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T THINK YOU'RE\NBETTER THAN US,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST 'CAUSE YOU GOT\NA FEW GOOD TEST SCORES.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'RE IN THE SIXTH GRADE,\NKID.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,WATCH YOUR MOUTH.\N- WATCH MY MOUTH?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.22,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU GUYS STUPID\NOR WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.22,Main,,0,0,0,,THE ONLY REASON PEOPLE\NCENSOR WHAT THEY SAY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.64,Main,,0,0,0,,IS TO BE RESPECTFUL.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.18,Main,,0,0,0,,AND WHY THE HELL WOULD I\NEVER WANT TO RESPECT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.85,Main,,0,0,0,,A GROUP OF IDIOTS LIKE YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU CAN'T SAY THAT.\NWE'RE OLDER THAN YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- TRUE. YEAH, YOU'RE A\NWHOLE YEAR OLDER THAN ME,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.65,Main,,0,0,0,,HOWEVER, I'M THE ONE\NWHO DID BETTER ON THAT TEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU GUYS ARE HILARIOUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SHOULD SHOW A LITTLE MORE\NRESPECT TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grunts )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- SAY THAT AGAIN,\NI DARE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU SURE ABOUT THIS?\NIF SOMETHING HAPPENS TO ME,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:37.66,Main,,0,0,0,,THE TEACHERS WILL\NDEFINITELY FIND OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, I AM THE BOY WONDER,\NAFTER ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,GET LOST.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( kids groan )\N- ALSO, I DON'T EVER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,WANT TO SEE YOU JERKS AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT KIDS LIKE\NTOTALLY PISSES ME OFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THINK WE SHOULD\NTEACH HIM A LESSON,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- SPECIFICALLY?\N- WELL, IF WE CAN'T TOUCH HIM,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.84,Main,,0,0,0,,WE CAN AT LEAST MESS WITH\NHIS LOCKER OR SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, THEN HE CAN'T\NRAT US OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- SOUNDS GOOD TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,LET'S TEACH THAT\NLITTLE PUNK SOME MANNERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( kids chuckle )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M HOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YAY.\NMY BABY BOY IS BACK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE A LITTLE LATE TODAY,\NAREN'T YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, I HAD TO FINISH UP\NSOME CLASS REP STUFF AT SCHOOL.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, WELL, I GUESS THAT\NDOES MAKE THE MOST SENSE,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT FOR SOME REASON\NI THOUGHT YOU WERE SPENDING
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.79,Main,,0,0,0,,A LITTLE QUALITY TIME WITH\NYOUR LOVELY FRIEND, SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY THE CRAP WOULD I WANT\NTO HANG OUT WITH SHOUKO?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,DON'T BE STUPID.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT I THOUGHT YOU\NTWO WERE FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU THOUGHT WRONG.\N- YOU SHOULD BE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT GIRL IS GOING TO BE\NINCREDIBLY GORGEOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:30.71,Main,,0,0,0,,WHEN SHE GETS\NA LITTLE OLDER.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,ALTHOUGH BY THAT TIME,\NIT MIGHT BE TOO LATE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,AND ALL YOU'LL BE LEFT WITH\NIS REGRET.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,ACCEPT IT, SHE'LL BE\NAS CUTE AS ME SOME DAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:40.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- LET IT GO, MOM. BESIDES,\NYOU'RE NOT THAT PRETTY ANYWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, THAT'S MEAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'LL BE LATE AGAIN TOMORROW.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH?  MORE WORK FOR\NYOUR CLASS AGAIN?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:49.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO. I HAVE A LITTLE\NSOMETHING
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I NEED TO TEACH\NSOME SIXTH GRADERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- SIXTH GRADERS?\N- LONG STORY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- OHH.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S WITH THE APRON?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:58.62,Main,,0,0,0,,PLEASE TELL ME YOU'RE\NNOT MAKING DINNER?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( chuckles )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M MAKING MEAT AND POTATO STEW.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.58,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S YOUR FAVORITE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'VE BEEN PEELING\NTHE SWEET POTATOES--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- MOM, YOU CAN'T PUT\NSWEET POTATOES IN A STEW!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT WHY NOT? I THOUGHT\NTHEY WERE BETTER FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.34,Main,,0,0,0,,THAN REGULAR POTATOES.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THEY DON'T\NGET AS SOFT EITHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY'RE SUPPOSED TO GET SOFT,\NAND I DON'T CARE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,IF THEY'RE BETTER\NFOR ME OR NOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.88,Main,,0,0,0,,( sighs ) AT LEAST IT\NMIGHT BE EDIBLE THIS TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH. I FORGOT TO BUY\NMEAT AT THE STORE,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I GUESS YOU COULD SAY\NWE'RE HAVING MEATLESS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.27,Main,,0,0,0,,MEAT AND POTATO STEW.\N- ARE YOU SAYING
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:25.06,Main,,0,0,0,,WE'RE JUST HAVING\NSTEAMED SWEET POTATOES?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji:\NSINCE THEY COULDN'T BEAT ME UP,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I KNEW THEY'D TRY TO\NDO SOMETHING TO MY STUFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT'S PROBABLY WHY I PROVOKED\NTHEM IN THE FIRST PLACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( chuckles )\NTHIS IS GONNA BE GREAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I GRABBED THE THINGS I DON'T\NWANT THEM TO MESS WITH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,FROM MY LOCKER AND\NKEPT THEM WITH ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji:\NI THOUGHT I'D KILL TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,UNTIL THE SIXTH GRADERS\NMADE THEIR MOVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.71,Main,,0,0,0,,ONCE THEY STARTED IN\NON MY LOCKER,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I PLANNED ON GOING\NTO GET A TEACHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,IN THE MEANTIME,\NI'LL START READING ANOTHER BOOK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: AT THAT TIME,\NI BELIEVED I WAS A HERO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,MOSTLY BECAUSE I ALSO BELIEVED\NI WAS BETTER THAN EVERYONE ELSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- WEIRD.\NWHERE'S SHOUKO BEEN ALL DAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:05.81,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE HASN'T FOLLOWED ME\NAROUND LIKE SHE USUALLY DOES.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Young Yuuji:\NBAKA AND TEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: BACK THEN,\NI SPENT AS MUCH TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,AS YUUJI WOULD LET ME\NFOLLOWING HIM AROUND.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T EVEN CARE\NTHAT HE WASN'T ALWAYS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.00,Main,,0,0,0,,VERY NICE TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,HE TREATED ME JUST LIKE\NHE TREATED EVERYONE ELSE,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I LIKED THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I WONDER IF\NYUUJI IS STILL HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.97,Main,,0,0,0,,HMM?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: I ENJOYED\NBEING AROUND HIM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I SIMPLY COULDN'T\NHELP MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- DAMN IT.\NNOT HERE EITHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT GUY'S SUCH A PUNK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW.\NMAYBE SOMEBODY ELSE DECIDED
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY WANTED TO\NHIDE HIS SHOES TOO,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,SO THEY JUST BEAT US\NTO THE PUNCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S POSSIBLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT NERD DOESN'T HAVE\NA LOT OF FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.78,Main,,0,0,0,,HE GETS PICKED ON\NALL THE TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- THERE'S PLENTY OF\NOTHER STUFF WE CAN MESS WITH.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DO YOU GUYS\NTHINK WE SHOULD WRITE?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW ABOUT "I LIKE TO\NCHEAT ON ALL MY TESTS"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,SOUND GOOD?\N- Both: HELL YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP THAT NOW!\N- ( boys gasp )
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:23.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- THOSE ARE--\NTHEY'RE NOT YOURS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT DO YOU WANT?\N- UM, WELL...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.48,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S JUST THAT\NTHOSE ARE YUUJI'S.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,AND YOU SHOULDN'T BE\NMESSING WITH THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?!\NTHIS IS NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,GET THE HELL OUT OF HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:39.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- I CAN'T DO THAT.\NYUUJI IS MY FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF YUUJI FINDS OUT\NWHAT I'M DOING,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,HE'S GOING TO BE\NSO MAD AT ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I THOUGHT...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,NONETHELESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE WRONG ABOUT THAT.\NSTOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DIDN'T THINK\NHE HAD ANY FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW.\NAND SHE'S A GIRL.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- COME ON, GUYS.\NWHO CARES ABOUT HER?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,LET'S JUST DO WHAT\NWE CAME HERE TO DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- GOOD POINT.\N- THIS IS GONNA BE AWESOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP IT!\N- HEY, LET GO OF ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THOUGHT YUUJI\NWOULD GET MAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I WAS AFRAID\NHE'D TELL THOSE BOYS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I WASN'T REALLY HIS FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grunts )\N- PLEASE STOP IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- ENOUGH ALREADY!\NGO AWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:14.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE'S CRAZY.\N- FOR REAL. WHAT'S HER PROBLEM?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE ASKING FOR\NIT, YOU KNOW THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT I DIDN'T CARE\NWHAT THEY SAID.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- LET GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( straining )\N- NO! ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, ARE YOU OKAY?\N- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,- AAH.  LOOK AT WHAT\NYOU DID TO MY NEW SHIRT,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU STUPID BRAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.42,Main,,0,0,0,,NOW I'M PISSED.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE DON'T. I'M SORRY.\N- IT'S TOO LATE FOR SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:50.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, I WONDER IF THEY'VE\NFALLEN INTO MY TRAP YET.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.68,Main,,0,0,0,,ALL RIGHT,\NTHEY'RE DOING IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( boys chattering )\N- NOT FUNNY!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,THE HELL'S GOING ON?\NWHY'S SHOUKO IN THERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,DON'T TELL ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT WAS OBVIOUS WHY\NSHOUKO HAD BEEN DRAGGED INTO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.74,Main,,0,0,0,,EITHER WAY, SHE NEEDED\NSOMEONE TO HELP HER OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HAVE TO SAVE HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES.  LIKE THE HERO\NTHAT I ALWAYS WANTED TO BE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,PLUS THOSE GUYS WERE\NALL PRACTICALLY IDIOTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS ME THAT WAS THE OVERLY\NINTELLIGENT SPECIAL ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,NOT TO MENTION, WE WERE\NIN COMPLETELY DIFFERENT LEAGUES,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,SO WHY HESITATE?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:25.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'LL BE FINE.\NDON'T BE SCARED.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,GUYS LIKE THEM...\NTHEY'RE NO BIG DEAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T KID YOURSELF, BUDDY.\NTHERE ARE THREE OF THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, I KNOW.\NI'LL GO GET A TEACHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT WHAT ABOUT SHOUKO?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE TEACHER'S GONNA\NTELL HER PARENTS,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THEN THEY'LL\NTHINK THEIR LITTLE GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,GETS PICKED ON ALL THE TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY'LL MAKE SHOUKO\NCHANGE SCHOOLS FOR SURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,( grunts ) WHATEVER. WHAT\NELSE AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S NOT LIKE IT HAS\NANYTHING TO DO WITH ME ANYWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ELSE CAN YOU DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU KNOW EXACTLY WHAT\NYOU CAN DO, YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grunts )\NMAN, THIS SUCKS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I JUST WANTED\NTO MAKE THEM PAY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR BEING SO MEAN TO ME!\N- OKAY, THEN PRETEND
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU DIDN'T SEE THIS\NAND WALK AWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU KNOW THERE'S\NNO WAY I CAN DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO MATTER WHAT\NCHOICE YOU MAKE,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE GONNA GET HURT.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.06,Main,,0,0,0,,ONE WAY OR ANOTHER,\NYOU'LL BE THE ONE WHO PAYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT BEING SAID, YOU'VE GOTTA\NDO WHAT YOU'VE GOTTA DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'RE TALKING ABOUT\NTHREE SIXTH GRADERS HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M NOT STRONG ENOUGH.\NNO WAY I CAN BEAT THOSE GUYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW DO YOU THINK\NSHOUKO FEELS ABOUT IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, BUT STILL...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW. GETTING BEAT UP\NIS PRETTY SCARY, ISN'T IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- OF COURSE, DUH!\N- I THOUGHT YOU WERE A HERO.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT A TRUE HERO WOULDN'T\NEXACTLY HESITATE, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,EVEN IF HE WAS TOTALLY\NSURE HE WAS GONNA LOSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,YEAH, HE'D DO IT.\N- SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.67,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT STUFF ONLY HAPPENS\NIN THE MOVIES, ASS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE THE ONE WHO'S\NBEEN ACTING BETTER THAN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,THOSE GUYS IN THE FIRST PLACE,\NRIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, YEAH, BUT THEIR SCORES--\N- IT'S NOT EASY BEING SMART,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.43,Main,,0,0,0,,IS IT?\NI KNOW HOW YOU FEEL.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT QUIT MAKING\NASININE EXCUSES
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.18,Main,,0,0,0,,AND TRYING TO FIND\NA WAY OUT OF THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO WHAT, ARE YOU TELLING ME\NIT'S BETTER TO BE AN IDIOT?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( chuckles )\NI GUESS SO.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,AN IDIOT WHO'D JUMP IN THERE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.11,Main,,0,0,0,,TO SAVE HER WITHOUT EVEN\NSTOPPING TO THINK?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,YEAH, HE'D BE A HELL OF\NA LOT COOLER THAN YOU ARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T GET IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T GET WHY ALL THIS\NIS HAPPENING TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING,\NSO WHY AM I THE ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:18.54,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO HAS TO SUFFER?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.71,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS ISN'T MY FAULT AT ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,IF ANYONE'S TO BLAME,\NIT'S THOSE GUYS FOR BEING
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,INSECURE JERKS,\NAND SHOUKO FOR BUTTING IN.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S THEIR FAULT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.30,Main,,0,0,0,,SO WHY IS THIS\NHAPPENING TO ME?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,( exhales )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.48,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S MORE...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.65,Main,,0,0,0,,SHOUKO SHOULD BE SCREAMING\NFOR HELP RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,ALL SHE HAS TO DO IS ASK.\NSAY IT, SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.32,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST SAY "SOMEBODY HELP ME"\NALREADY,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.16,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THEN EVEN IF\NTHE TEACHERS FIND OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.74,Main,,0,0,0,,AND HER PARENTS MAKE HER\NCHANGE SCHOOLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S ALL BECAUSE OF HER,\NNOT ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S STILL NOT MY FAULT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.08,Main,,0,0,0,,YEAH.  THAT WORKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.96,Main,,0,0,0,,COME ON, SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- Young Shouko: STOP.\N- SAY IT.  ASK FOR HELP.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:09.51,Main,,0,0,0,,CHANGING SCHOOLS IS BETTER\NTHAN BEING PICKED ON, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.76,Main,,0,0,0,,ALL YOU HAVE TO DO IS ASK.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:13.76,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST SAY THE WORDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.35,Main,,0,0,0,,ASK FOR HELP.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:17.68,Main,,0,0,0,,SAY IT.  SAY IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:18.93,Main,,0,0,0,,SAY IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WON'T.\NI WON'T SAY IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.27,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY'LL MAKE ME\NCHANGE SCHOOLS AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.36,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,HEY, YOU GUYS ARE\NA BUNCH OF JERKS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( boys gasp )\N- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT THE HELL\NARE YOU DOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T YOU ASSHOLES REALIZE\NHOW CRAZY PATHETIC YOU ALL ARE?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.55,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT KIND OF GUY\NBEATS UP ON A GIRL?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:53.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- SAKAMOTO?\N- LOOK WHO DECIDED TO SHOW UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- COME ON,\NLET'S GO HOME, SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT.  SORRY, BRO.\NNOT SO FAST.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU TWO AREN'T\NGOING ANYWHERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )\N- YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHOUKO IS GOING HOME.\N- BUT--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOW.\N- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'LL GO GET A TEACHER.\N- NO, DON'T BE AN IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.24,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST GO HOME.\NI DON'T WANT YOU HERE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,GETTING IN MY WAY.\N- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,YEAH, OKAY THEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M GONNA GO HOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( shouting )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji:\NTHAT WAS THE DAY I REALIZED
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW IMMATURE\NI REALLY WAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'D NEVER FELT SO MISERABLE,\NPITIFUL, AND EMBARRASSED.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( boys grunting )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: AFTER SEEING YUUJI'S\NSHOULDERS TREMBLING LIKE THAT,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:48.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS SO MAD AT MYSELF\NFOR NOT BEING ABLE TO HELP.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: I CREATED A REASON FOR\NSHOUKO TO GET THE WRONG IDEA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS ALL A MISTAKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.45,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS MY RESPONSIBILITY\NAND I HAVE TO MAKE UP FOR IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( shouts )
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT WASN'T.\NYOU'RE WRONG, YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE'S MORE TO OUR STORY.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU JUST NEVER KNEW.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, LOOK WHO'S BACK HOME.\NHEY THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I GOT A CALL FROM\NTHE SCHOOL EARLIER.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.73,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU GONNA BE OKAY?\N- I'M FINE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,EVERYTHING'S FINE.\N- OH, NO, HONEY.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.90,Main,,0,0,0,,OBVIOUSLY THAT IS NOT TRUE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.95,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY TOLD ME THAT\NYOU GOT INTO A FIGHT TODAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT CAN I SAY? A COUPLE\NOF GUYS PISSED ME OFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, ARE YOU SURE\NTHAT'S ALL THERE IS TO IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, THAT'S ALL.\NTHEY PISSED ME OFF,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I PUNCHED THEM.\NWILL YOU PLEASE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:48.96,Main,,0,0,0,,GET OFF MY BACK ALREADY?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:53.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY MADE YOU MAD,\NRIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:59.76,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S MY FAULT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,HE WAS ONLY\NTRYING TO PROTECT ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.18,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'VE ALREADY\NTOLD ME WHAT HAPPENED,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:08.02,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I PROMISE YOU, EVERYTHING\NIS GOING TO BE ALL RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:11.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW CAN IT BE? HE'S GONNA\NBE KNOWN AS A BAD KID.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.69,Main,,0,0,0,,AND HE WON'T GET THAT\NRECOMMENDATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR JUNIOR HIGH NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( chuckles )\NI DON'T CARE ABOUT ALL THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,OH, SHOUKO, LISTEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:21.28,Main,,0,0,0,,YUUJI FOUND OUT\NTHERE'S MORE TO HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.87,Main,,0,0,0,,THAN JUST BEING A SMART KID.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,WITHOUT YOU, HE NEVER COULD\NHAVE REALIZED THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I'M ACTUALLY\NVERY GRATEFUL.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )\NHMM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( chuckles )\N- MRS. SAKAMOTO?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS IT, SHOUKO?\NI'M ALL EARS.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- UM, WHEN I GROW UP...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.63,Main,,0,0,0,,WELL, I'M GOING\NTO MARRY YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU POSITIVE?\NIT IS A BIG DECISION.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- I PROMISE I'LL\NMAKE HIM HAPPY.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( chuckles )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,IF YOU WANT TO KNOW\NTHE TRUTH, DEAR,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT'S REALLY SOMETHING\NHE SHOULD SAY TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I WON'T DISAGREE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, I'LL TELL YOU WHAT,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'LL DO WHATEVER I CAN\NTO MAKE SURE HE SAYS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,THE VERY SAME LINE\NTO YOU ONE DAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:21:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- REALLY?\N- YES, REALLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,NOW THAT IS OF COURSE\NAS LONG AS YOU DON'T
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,STOP LIKING HIM\NSO MUCH BY THEN, 'KAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:07.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, I WON'T.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I PROMISE.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:17.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I WILL LIKE YUUJI FOREVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:22.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( theme music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:33.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:54.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: QUESTION 12,\NWHAT DO YOU CALL IT WHEN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,A MYSTERIOUS GROUP\NSTAKES CLAIM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:58.19,Main,,0,0,0,,TO A SPECIFIC PLACE\NFOR NO REASON?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- DUDES WHO ARE POPULAR WITH\NCHICKS ARE OUR SWORN ENEMIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: I'M TALKING\NABOUT YOU, BY THE WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: NEXT EPISODE,\NIDIOTS, CLOWNERY, AND REQUIEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.36,0:24:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara:\NTHIS WILL BE ON THE TEST.
